Class ProjectContact

java.lang.Object
ProjectContact
public class ProjectContact
extends java.lang.Object
Class to create a Project Contact object.

Project Contact objects are attributes for Project objects. Project Contact objects and Project objects are managed by the Poise class.

Author:
Lindsey
See Also:
Project, Poise
